            {
              "message": "P1, convention contradiction: both [`.harness/catalogue-lint/config.json`](./home/flip451/individual/t-rust/templates/SoTOHE-core-003/.harness/catalogue-lint/config.json#L123) and [`.harness/catalogue-lint/presets/ddd-strict.json`](./home/flip451/individual/t-rust/templates/SoTOHE-core-003/.harness/catalogue-lint/presets/ddd-strict.json#L123) hardcode the six layer names in `ForbidPrimitiveInTypes.layers`. ADR `2026-07-01-0004` D6/D7 says the default config must be generated from `architecture-rules.json` and not hardcoded, so this will drift from the layer SSoT and can miss future `tddd.enabled` layers unless both files are manually kept in sync.",
